<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:8.5423in'>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>最左匹配原则是指在一个复合条件查询语句中，会先检查最左侧的条件，如果这个条件能够使用索引进行匹配，那么就会使用索引来提高查询效率，如果不能使用索引，那么就会扫描整张表来查找匹配的记录</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>多列索引是基于多个字段的索引，它可以同时按照多个字段进行查找操作。由于</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树的这些性质，它只能根据一个键值来进行构建。如果要根据多个键值来构建</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树，那么就需要对每个键值都构建一个独立的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树，这样就会造成大量的空间浪费和维护成本。因此，因此在构建多列索引时，数据库会使用多列索引中最左边的字段来构建</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>B+</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>树，这样就可以支持多个字段的查找操作了。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#24292F'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#24292F'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'>最左匹配原则和多列索引的索引存储结构和检索方式是有关。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>在多列索引中，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>a</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引是有序排列，而</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>b</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引是无序排列。</span></li>
 <ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>当查询条件为</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> b = 2 </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>时，没有办法利用索引，因为</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>b</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>是无序的。</span></li>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'
      lang=zh-CN>当查询条件中不存在</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=en-US> a</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'
      lang=zh-CN>，索引失效。</span></li>
 </ul>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MySQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>引擎在执行查询时，为了更好地利用索引，在查询过程中会动态调整查询字段的顺序，使其满足最左匹配。因此在多列索引（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>last_name</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>, </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>first_name</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）中，以下两种查询都可以使用索引。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#0077AA'>SELECT </span><span style='color:#A67F59'>*
</span><span style='color:#0077AA'>FROM</span><span style='color:black'>
test<br>
</span><span style='color:#0077AA'>WHERE</span><span style='color:black'>
last_name</span><span style='color:#A67F59'>=</span><span style='color:#669900'>'Jones'
</span><span style='color:#A67F59'>AND</span><span style='color:black'>
first_name</span><span style='color:#A67F59'>=</span><span style='color:#669900'>'John'</span><span
style='color:#909090'>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#70AD47'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#0077AA'>SELECT </span><span style='color:#A67F59'>*
</span><span style='color:#0077AA'>FROM</span><span style='color:black'>
test<br>
</span><span style='color:#0077AA'>WHERE</span><span style='color:black'>
first_name</span><span style='color:#A67F59'>=</span><span style='color:#669900'>'John'
</span><span style='color:#A67F59'>AND</span><span style='color:black'>
last_name</span><span style='color:#A67F59'>=</span><span style='color:#669900'>'Jones'</span><span
style='color:#909090'>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#909090'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>在范围查询</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>(&gt;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>、</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>&lt;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>、</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5'
     lang=en-US>BETWEEN</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>、</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>LIKE</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>)</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>下，索引的最左匹配原则会一直向右匹配直到遇到范围查询停止，即范围查询最左边的字段可以匹配索引，之后的字段无法使用索引，会被忽略，索引失效。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MySQL</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>5.6</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>版本之后开启了索引条件下推优化</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，后面的索引列会加入全索引扫描用于筛选，因此索引生效。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>范围查询无法完全使用最左匹配原则的原因是，最左匹配原则只能处理等值比较。在等值比较中，我们只需要比较一个值是否等于另一个值，因此只需要比较一个列。但是，在范围查询中，我们需要比较一个值是否在某个范围内，这需要比较多个值，因此无法完全使用最左匹配原则。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>假设有多列索引（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>age, sex</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>），</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>age</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>可以使用索引，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>sex</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>不能使用索引。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'
     lang=zh-CN>只使用了</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
     12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=en-US> age </span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=zh-CN>索引来选择行</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#0077AA' lang=zh-CN>SELECT </span><span
style='color:#A67F59' lang=zh-CN>* </span><span style='color:#0077AA'
lang=zh-CN>FROM </span><span style='color:black' lang=en-US>user</span><span
style='color:black' lang=zh-CN><br>
</span><span style='color:#0077AA' lang=zh-CN>WHERE </span><span
style='color:black' lang=en-US>age &gt; </span><span style='color:#669900'
lang=en-US>20</span><span style='color:#669900' lang=zh-CN> </span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-size:12.0pt'><span

style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#669900' lang=zh-CN>'</span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";color:#669900' lang=zh-CN>男</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#669900' lang=zh-CN>'</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#909090' lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

lang=zh-CN>FROM </span><span style='color:black' lang=en-US>user</span><span

</span><span style='color:#0077AA' lang=zh-CN>WHERE </span><span

lang=en-US>20</span><span style='color:#669900' lang=zh-CN> </span></p>

</span><span style='color:#0077AA' lang=zh-CN>WHERE </span><span

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#24292E'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'
     lang=zh-CN>最左匹配原则适用于</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>LIKE </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'
     lang=zh-CN>语句，但只有</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>LIKE</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'
     lang=zh-CN> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
     12.0pt;color:#70AD47' lang=zh-CN>&quot;XXX%&quot;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'
     lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=zh-CN>的情况索引生效，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#2E75B5'
     lang=en-US>LIKE</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
     12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=zh-CN> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47' lang=zh-CN>&quot;%XXX&quot;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'
     lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=zh-CN>索引失效。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#24292E'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=zh-CN>假设有多列索引（</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:black' lang=en-US>name, sex</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=zh-CN>），</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
     12.0pt;color:black' lang=en-US>name </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=en-US>sex </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";

     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E'
     lang=zh-CN>只使用了</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:

     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#24292E' lang=zh-CN>索引来选择行</span></li>
</ul>
